      <div style="font-size:11px; color:var(--textSec); line-height:1.7;">• 1 m/s = 3.6 km/h<br>• 1 km/h = 0.278 m/s<br>• 1h = 60 min = 3600 sec<br>• 30 min = 0.5 h</div>
    </div>
